HEADWORD: Metamorphist
<hw>Met`a*mor"phist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Eccl.)</fld>
<def>One who believes that the body of Christ was merged into the Deity
when he ascended.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

